  "body": "Fee recipient is changed when running mev boost, it seems builders can change the header and add different fee recipient which effectively steals the block tips and the mev fees as well.  \r\n\r\nThe message I get on lighthouse beacon client is:\r\n\r\n`INFO Fee recipient from connected builder does not match, using it anyways., service: exec`\r\n\r\nSo far I have identified this probelm on goerli, this is the address of one known attacker: 0x9B3F8604D2F20a2F864Cd209e02c37e7C9997681\r\n\r\n",
